d: #FFFFFF; color: #1A1A1A; padding: 48px; border-radius: 16px; margin: 0 auto 48px; max-width: 900px; box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);">                <h3 style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 800; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 24px; color: #0A2463;">                    🤝 What We're Building Together                </h3>                                <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;">                    This isn't just about more clients. <strong style="color: #0A2463;">It's about fighting a corrupt system.</strong>                </p>                                <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 32px;">                    <!-- The Problem -->                    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 32px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #DC2626;">                        <div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">⚖️</div>                        <h4 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1A1A1A;">The System Is Rigged</h4>                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #333;">                            Insurance companies use databases like <strong>Colossus</strong> (containing <strong>over 11 million claims</strong>)                             to systematically lowball settlements against solo and small firms. They know you don't have the data they do                              and they use that <strong>$50+ billion advantage</strong> against you in every negotiation.                        </p>                    </div>                                        <!-- The Solution -->                    <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 32px; border-radius: 12px; border-left: 4px solid #10B981;">                        <div style="font-size: 48px; margin-bottom: 16px;">🛡️</div>                        <h4 style="font-size: 22px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 16px; color: #1A1A1A;">We're Fighting Back</h4>                        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.7; color: #333;">                            TrueVow Founding Members help populate an <strong>anonymous settlement database</strong>  leveling the playing field.                             <strong>It takes 1 minute per case</strong> to enter outcome data (no sensitive info required).                             Each entry earns you <strong>settlement credits</strong> that unlock future queries for your own cases.                        </p>                    </div>                </div>                                <div style="background: rgba(255,255,255,0.1); padding: 24px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 24px; border: 2px solid rgba(16,185,129,0.3);">                    <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; margin: 0;">                        <strong style="color: #0A2463;">How settlement credits work:</strong> Enter 10 anonymous settlements ➡️ Earn 10 credits ➡️ Use credits to query "What's the average settlement for a rear-end collision with soft tissue injury in Miami-Dade?"                         You contribute, you benefit  it's a true co-op model.                    </p>                </div>                                <div style="background: #F8F9FA; padding: 32px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 32px; border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);">                    <p style="font-size: 18px; line-height: 1.8; text-align: center; margin: 0; font-style: italic;">                        <strong>"This isn't a transaction. It's a movement."</strong><br>                        <span style="font-size: 16px; color: #666;">                             As Seth Godin says, we're building something <strong>remarkable</strong> together.<br>                             Something that brings <strong>revolutionary change</strong> to legal tech.<br>                             Something that <strong>actually helps</strong> solo and small firms win.                        </span>                    </p>                </div>            </div>                        <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-top: 40px;">                <!-- Left Column: Who Qualifies -->                <div style="background: white; padding: 40px; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">                    <h3 style="font-size: 24px; font-weight: 800; color: #0A2463; margin-bottom: 24px;">                        ✅ Who Qualifies as a Founding Member?                    </h3>                    <p style="color: #666; margin-bottom: 16px;">You must:</p>                    <ul style="color: #666; line-height: 1.8;">                        <li>Complete onboarding successfully</li>                        <li>Maintain <strong>at least 1 qualified booking per month</strong></li>                        <li>Adhere to TrueVow's ethical guidelines (no spam, no misuse)</li>                    </ul>                                        <div style="background: #E8F4FD; padding: 20px; border-radius: 12px; margin-top: 24px; border-left: 4px solid #0A2463;">                        <p style="color: #0A2463; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;">                            ⚠️ Important:                        </p>                        <p style="color: #666; font-size: 15px;">                            Founding Members <strong>count toward the 33% cap</strong> in their county  they are <strong>not a separate pool</strong>.                             They are simply the <strong>first firms to claim spots</strong> within that cap.                        </p>                    </div>                                        <!-- Total Value Box -->                        <div style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0A2463 0%, #1E40AF 100%); color: white; padding: 32px; border-radius: 16px; margin: 32px 0 24px; text-align: center; box-shadow: 0 8px